19
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:19,800
<i>Are you really Onee-chan? (big sister)</i>

20
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:23,000
<i>Asuka, I'm sorry.</i>

21
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:39,600
As always, you roll around so much in your sleep.

22
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,200
Minami-kun...

23
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:55,700
Hurry up and get up. We'll be late.

24
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,800
Were you watching me?

25
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:01,830
How can you sleep like that.

26
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:06,000
- I'm changing, so look away.<br>- Okay.

27
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:10,200
<i>It's been 4 weeks since I became small.</i>

28
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:12,400
<i>A lot has happened...</i>

29
00:02:13,410 --> 00:02:14,750
Here you go.

30
00:02:16,250 --> 00:02:18,080
Thank you for the meal.

31
