181
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:55,740
<i>[When I am in his pocket, I am the closest person to him.]</i>

182
00:11:56,750 --> 00:12:00,270
<i>[I feel his body heat and heartbeat, ]</i>

183
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:06,470
<i>[and I can get closer to him than any other women of his kind.]</i>

184
00:12:06,470 --> 00:12:11,310
<i>[I am the closest to him, and yet, I am the farthest.]</i>

185
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:15,110
<i>[Every time I dream of my wish coming true,]</i>

186
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:19,950
<i>[I deny the possibility, thinking that Big Guy <br>wouldn't possibly love me.]</i>

187
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:24,720
<i>[That's what I force myself to think.]</i>

188
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,150
<i>[I'll be happy just to be beside him.]</i>

189
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:33,220
