<i>I am Takagi. I'm Shunichi-kun's classmate.</i>

197
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:48,390
Takagi?!

198
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,040
Why is he here?

199
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:52,470
<i>Oh, welcome.</i>

200
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:56,340
<i>Shunichi, Takagi-kun is here.</i>

201
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:58,650
<i>Come down.</i>

202
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:02,020
<i>Shunichi-kun's room is upstairs, right?</i>

203
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:04,820
<i>It's okay. I am going to his room.</i>

204
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:05,450
Huh?

205
00:14:05,450 --> 00:14:07,310
<i>Oh, really?</i>

206
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:10,990
Hey, hide somewhere.

207
00:14:10,990 --> 00:14:12,280
Okay.

208
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,140
What's the matter?

209
00:14:24,140 --> 00:14:26,430
Why did you come here all of a sudden?

210
00:14:26,430 --> 00:14:29,460
I want to talk to you as a man, face to face.

211
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,680
Let me come in.

212
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,530
Hey!

213
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:42,630
I was studying right now.

214
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:45,390
- Make it short if you need to talk.<br>- Your figurine doll...

215
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:49,050
Does she sleep here at night?

216
00:14:49,050 --> 00:14:52,380
Oh! Well...

217
00:14:52,380 --> 00:14:53,920
This is actually...

218
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:57,240
That is undoubtedly a bed for a figurine!

219
00:14:57,240 --> 00:15:00,870
What? What are you saying?

220
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:04,330
I just put a towel in it. That's all.

221
00:15:04,330 --> 00:15:06,190
You are playing dumb?

222
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:09,940
Then, shall I put my figurine on it?

223
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:15,870
Look. It's just the right size!

224
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:19,840
Hey, what are you talking about?

225
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:24,020
