226
00:15:24,020 --> 00:15:25,950
Don't try to deny it.

227
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:32,850
I saw Horikiri-shi peeking out of your pocket in the classroom.

228
00:15:32,850 --> 00:15:35,360
- What?<br>- What?

229
00:15:36,610 --> 00:15:38,900
That was really well made.

230
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:48,830
<i>Riku thought I was a figurine.</i>

231
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:50,890
That's fine.

232
00:15:50,890 --> 00:15:54,190
That's not what I want to ask you the most.

233
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:57,860
Minami.

234
00:16:00,330 --> 00:16:02,720
You love Horikiri-shi, don't you?

235
00:16:03,950 --> 00:16:05,850
<i>Riku...</i>

236
00:16:07,490 --> 00:16:10,620
I can tell because I like creating things.

237
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:16,200
The reason why you can make a figurine that looks so real is because you love her that much.

238
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:22,900
W-What are you saying?

